Currently, when a record reaches the final status in the Path for Waivers and Decisions, the entire path bar appears green.

Requirement is to modify the behavior so that only the current (latest) stage is displayed in blue when the record is in the final (end-of-path) status, instead of showing green.

All other stages and statuses should retain existing behavior.

For intermediate statuses → Path behaves as-is (green progression).
When record reaches final status:
Only the current stage is highlighted in blue
Previous stages remain unchanged (green)
Change applies to both Waivers and Decisions objects.
No impact to path structure, stages, or navigation.
UI change is reflected consistently on Lightning record pages.
